- Great success!
- Great success!

58
00:03:50,185 --> 00:03:51,379
...like that.

59
00:03:52,821 --> 00:03:55,346
Or if it's not that,
are you guys up to something?

60
00:03:56,358 --> 00:03:59,122
Wh-Wh-What are you saying?!

61
00:04:00,528 --> 00:04:02,894
K-Kakashi Sensei, we're celebrating
your release from the hospital!

62
00:04:03,365 --> 00:04:07,028
N-Now! P-P-P-lease eat, eat!

63
00:04:07,969 --> 00:04:11,700
All right...
Then I'll eat it without hesitation.

64
00:04:12,274 --> 00:04:12,933
Thank you for waiting.

65
00:04:13,008 --> 00:04:14,475
The pork slices are our treat.

66
00:04:25,387 --> 00:04:26,820
Thanks for the treat.

67
00:04:30,158 --> 00:04:33,150
Oh! Sasuke...
What a coincidence!

68
00:04:34,329 --> 00:04:35,455
Get away! Ino Pig!

69
00:04:35,530 --> 00:04:36,497
Wha?!

70
00:04:36,631 --> 00:04:38,724
Aw man! I can't see at all!

71
00:04:39,234 --> 00:04:42,362
I'm finished! That was good...

72
00:04:42,604 --> 00:04:43,366
- So fast!
- So fast!

73
00:04:43,905 --> 00:04:45,634
Huh? Something wrong

74
00:04:47,275 --> 00:04:48,572
N-Nothing's wrong

75
00:04:48,643 --> 00:04:49,337
Hey!

76
00:04:50,178 --> 00:04:51,042
- Huh?
- Huh?

77
00:04:54,749 --> 00:04:57,309
- Wow! I'm really curious!
- Wow! I'm really curious!

78
00:05:02,057 --> 00:05:06,391
Now, I will <i>not</i> allow myself
to be denied a glimpse of him!

79
00:05:06,661 --> 00:05:08,925
But how are you
going to see it?

80
00:05:09,197 --> 00:05:10,221
That's...

81
00:05:11,266 --> 00:05:13,530
We'll see it somehow...

82
00:05:13,601 --> 00:05:15,592
I'm asking you how! You idiot!

83
00:05:16,905 --> 00:05:20,636
Then, then, do you have
a good plan, Sakura?

84
00:05:20,942 --> 00:05:21,931
That's...

85
00:05:22,043 --> 00:05:24,102
We'll follow by completely marking him.

86
00:05:24,546 --> 00:05:26,377
If we do that, he'll eventually
take his mask off.

87
00:05:26,648 --> 00:05:28,639
Sasuke, you are really bright.

88
00:05:29,017 --> 00:05:31,611
What's that big deal?
That was so average!

89
00:05:31,686 --> 00:05:32,778
Did you say something?

90
00:05:33,321 --> 00:05:34,879
Well, that's fine.

91
00:05:45,066 --> 00:05:47,694
What's Kakashi Sensei doing?

92
00:05:48,436 --> 00:05:49,596
I'm disappointed in him.

93
00:05:50,939 --> 00:05:51,837
He noticed us!

94
00:05:52,273 --> 00:05:54,833
Stupid Naruto!
We were found because of you!

95
00:05:54,943 --> 00:05:56,672
I tell you it's not my fault!

96
00:05:56,978 --> 00:05:57,672
What?!

97
00:05:59,614 --> 00:06:02,208
I-It's being made into a movie?!

98
00:06:04,152 --> 00:06:06,120
I'm going to go buy
an advance ticket.

99
00:06:06,488 --> 00:06:07,978
Hey, he's begun to move!

100
00:06:08,256 --> 00:06:09,314
We'll follow his track!

101
00:06:09,891 --> 00:06:10,653
Yeah!

102
00:06:14,462 --> 00:06:16,089
What? He's gone!

103
00:06:17,165 --> 00:06:18,996
Darn, he got away...

104
00:06:19,134 --> 00:06:21,932
Darn it, where did he go?

105
00:06:22,003 --> 00:06:23,834
What are you guys doing?

106
00:06:25,206 --> 00:06:27,231
Do you guys have
some business with me?

107
00:06:27,308 --> 00:06:29,139
- N-Not really...
- N-Not really...

108
00:06:36,184 --> 00:06:39,813
Hey, how did he find us out?

109
00:06:40,155 --> 00:06:42,020
Isn't it because there
are too many of us?

110
00:06:43,525 --> 00:06:46,153
If the presence is erased,
the number of people shouldn't matter!

111
00:06:46,561 --> 00:06:49,792
Or... have you forgotten the Jutsu?
Sakura...

112
00:06:49,864 --> 00:06:51,559
That's you!

113
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:54,130
It will be good training to shadow him.

114
00:06:54,836 --> 00:06:56,565
From now on,
we'll go about it individually.

115
00:06:56,771 --> 00:07:00,207
Y-Yeah, let's just leave Naruto here!

116
00:07:00,909 --> 00:07:01,807
What?!

117
00:07:05,413 --> 00:07:10,908
And Junko then says...
"Oh, I am losing you."

118
00:07:22,997 --> 00:07:24,726
What? What?

119
00:07:34,275 --> 00:07:35,401
He got away...

120
00:07:35,710 --> 00:07:37,473
Clumsy as usual...

121
00:07:37,812 --> 00:07:39,074
You idiot...

122
00:07:39,814 --> 00:07:40,644
Sorry.

123
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:54,060
Gosh, what is Kakashi Sensei doing?

124
00:07:54,128 --> 00:07:56,596
He hasn't moved for
such a long time...

125
00:07:58,533 --> 00:07:59,397
No way!

126
00:08:21,556 --> 00:08:22,887
Sasuke! How did it go?!

127
00:08:24,792 --> 00:08:26,282
No more shadowing

128
00:08:37,238 --> 00:08:38,671
Off we go!

129
00:08:39,407 --> 00:08:41,671
<i>Today's mission is to help at a farm.</i>

130
00:08:42,343 --> 00:08:44,208
<i>The mission itself is not a big deal.</i>

131
00:08:44,812 --> 00:08:47,178
<i>We're definitely going to look at it...</i>

132
00:08:47,549 --> 00:08:49,574
- <i>Kakashi Sensei's real face!</i>
- <i>Kakashi Sensei's real face!</i>

133
00:08:52,554 --> 00:08:53,885
What's the matter?

134
00:08:53,955 --> 00:08:55,786
You guys seem to have
lots of energy today.

135
00:08:56,057 --> 00:08:57,991
- I have lots of energy!
- I'm ready to go!

136
00:08:59,727 --> 00:09:02,195
Oh, that's excellent.

137
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:08,168
I've finally found you...

138
00:09:11,372 --> 00:09:13,135
Kakashi Hatake!

139
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:17,539
Kakashi...

140
00:09:18,613 --> 00:09:20,376
It has been a long while,

141
00:09:20,448 --> 00:09:23,042
but I will settle
my long standing grudge!

142
00:09:23,151 --> 00:09:25,142
Boss, what is your grudge?

143
00:09:26,454 --> 00:09:28,547
Fool! Have you forgotten?!

144
00:09:29,591 --> 00:09:30,956
I cannot forget.

145
00:09:31,259 --> 00:09:34,057
It happened in the spring
of three years ago...

146
00:09:34,228 --> 00:09:35,320
No!

147
00:09:35,463 --> 00:09:37,727
You don't need to be that scared.

148
00:09:38,032 --> 00:09:39,294
No!

149
00:09:40,268 --> 00:09:43,567
Our boss says he has something
to talk to you about...

150
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,867
Your boss?!

151
00:09:56,584 --> 00:09:59,644
I love you... Please marry me!

152
00:09:59,854 --> 00:10:01,845
- Boss is so cool!
- Boss is so cool!

153
00:10:01,923 --> 00:10:02,787
No...

154
00:10:02,991 --> 00:10:04,720
There's no need to be embarrassed.

155
00:10:05,093 --> 00:10:08,585
You can be honest and
fly into my arms.

156
00:10:10,565 --> 00:10:11,532
No...

157
00:10:12,166 --> 00:10:15,033
Don't worry.
Even though I look like this,

158
00:10:15,536 --> 00:10:17,197
I have a tidy sum of money!

159
00:10:17,271 --> 00:10:19,102
I am telling you, no!

160
00:10:19,407 --> 00:10:23,070
What? You're turning me down
in these surroundings?

161
00:10:23,811 --> 00:10:25,779
When I say no, I mean no!

162
00:10:26,247 --> 00:10:29,580
I made it such a romantic setting,
but why?

163
00:10:29,684 --> 00:10:31,549
I don't like what I don't like!

164
00:10:31,686 --> 00:10:33,654
Why don't you stop it around there?

165
00:10:33,955 --> 00:10:34,785
- Huh?
- Huh?

166
00:10:37,425 --> 00:10:40,952
Hey, the girl doesn't like it
and no matter how you look at it,

167
00:10:41,029 --> 00:10:43,156
you're being rejected, buddy.

168
00:10:43,398 --> 00:10:44,660
Yeah, yeah.

169
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:46,630
You're pretty gutsy.

170
00:10:47,135 --> 00:10:49,330
Do you understand who we are?!

171
00:10:50,605 --> 00:10:53,972
Are you challenging us, knowing that
we are the Moya Ninja Threesome...

172
00:10:54,042 --> 00:10:55,805
fearsome enough to silence
a crying child?!

173
00:10:56,611 --> 00:10:59,136
Moya Ninja? Never heard of it.

174
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:01,539
You don't know Moya Ninja?!

175
00:11:01,616 --> 00:11:03,777
How dare you make fools of us!

176
00:11:03,918 --> 00:11:05,385
Who the hell are you?

177
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:07,913
It's not worth enough to introduce, but...

178
00:11:08,356 --> 00:11:10,290
Well, my name is Kakashi Hatake.

179
00:11:10,358 --> 00:11:11,882
- You're introducing yourself!
- You're introducing yourself!

180
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:13,158
Hey you...

181
00:11:13,227 --> 00:11:14,785
You're going to regret it.

182
00:11:14,929 --> 00:11:18,092
For getting in the way of
someone's romance!

183
00:11:18,566 --> 00:11:19,533
Romance?

184
00:11:20,501 --> 00:11:22,332
Isn't it just an annoying,
one sided love?

185
00:11:23,471 --> 00:11:24,938
Enough!

186
00:11:25,573 --> 00:11:27,336
Men! We're going to attack!

187
00:11:27,408 --> 00:11:28,170
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

188
00:11:28,342 --> 00:11:30,537
4... 3... 2... 1...

189
00:11:30,812 --> 00:11:32,575
- Hustle! Hustle!
- Hustle! Hustle!

190
00:11:41,622 --> 00:11:44,455
Please! Somebody help me!

191
00:11:44,525 --> 00:11:45,822
Hey! I can't stand heights!

192
00:11:45,893 --> 00:11:46,985
I'll take you back to the village.

193
00:11:47,061 --> 00:11:47,993
Stop talking! Hey!

194
00:11:48,062 --> 00:11:51,031
Hey, quit sighing!
What, are you just leaving us here?!

195
00:11:52,133 --> 00:11:54,328
That's how it went...

196
00:11:54,402 --> 00:11:55,334
- Don't be so proud!
- Don't be so proud!

197
00:11:55,403 --> 00:11:56,529
- You lost!
- You lost!

198
00:11:57,205 --> 00:11:59,673
So it means revenge from
three years ago

199
00:11:59,874 --> 00:12:01,899
Boss has become stronger
in the last three years,

200
00:12:01,976 --> 00:12:04,638
and he's going to beat him up
in a face to face match!

201
00:12:05,046 --> 00:12:06,377
That's so dramatic!

202
00:12:07,749 --> 00:12:10,547
Fool! Who would take such risk?!

203
00:12:10,752 --> 00:12:11,377
Huh?

204
00:12:12,453 --> 00:12:13,511
If we're going to do it,

205
00:12:13,588 --> 00:12:16,523
we'll do it stealthily from
the shadows! Stealthily.

206
00:12:18,526 --> 00:12:20,255
- D-Dirty!
- D-Dirty!

207
00:12:22,630 --> 00:12:23,995
Welcome!

208
00:12:24,065 --> 00:12:26,863
Welcome! Welcome! Welcome!

209
00:12:26,934 --> 00:12:28,128
Welcome!

210
00:12:34,542 --> 00:12:35,440
Incredible!

211
00:12:36,244 --> 00:12:37,370
Looks delicious!

212
00:12:37,678 --> 00:12:38,702
How extravagant.

213
00:12:40,515 --> 00:12:41,846
Please take your time...

214
00:12:47,722 --> 00:12:49,280
<i>Kakashi...</i>

215
00:12:49,357 --> 00:12:52,053
<i>Now eat, this will be</i>
<i>your last dinner party.</i>

216
00:12:53,027 --> 00:12:55,655
<i>That meal contains</i>
<i>a tasteless and odorless medicine</i>

217
00:12:55,730 --> 00:12:59,097
<i>that causes uncontrollable hiccups.</i>

218
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:03,666
<i>Just keep on having</i>
<i>the ceaseless hiccups and die suffering!</i>

219
00:13:04,839 --> 00:13:07,672
<i>It's a fitting end for you!</i>

220
00:13:10,511 --> 00:13:13,071
Something wrong?

221
00:13:13,481 --> 00:13:15,073
Not one of you has
even laid chopsticks on the food.

222
00:13:15,349 --> 00:13:19,376
Not really, but why don't you,
Kakashi Sensei, hurry up and eat?

223
00:13:19,687 --> 00:13:22,383
Well, I'm on a diet.

224
00:13:22,857 --> 00:13:25,018
<i>Figured he'd say something like that.</i>

225
00:13:25,159 --> 00:13:29,061
<i>Then I'll strip off that mask</i>
<i>if it kills me!</i>

226
00:13:30,331 --> 00:13:31,923
My hands slipped...

227
00:13:47,014 --> 00:13:48,481
How could you!

228
00:13:48,616 --> 00:13:50,811
Oh, sorry, sorry, I unintentionally...

229
00:13:50,885 --> 00:13:52,819
- What do you mean "unintentionally"?!
- What do you mean "unintentionally"?!

230
00:13:53,421 --> 00:13:56,015
What a pity! The meal...

231
00:13:56,157 --> 00:13:58,523
- How could he do such a thing
- How could he do such a thing

232
00:14:01,829 --> 00:14:02,887
Hey, what's the next move?

233
00:14:03,297 --> 00:14:05,788
Don't worry. I have an idea.

234
00:14:06,534 --> 00:14:07,558
- An idea?
- An idea?

235
00:14:14,942 --> 00:14:18,070
I see, this is pretty good thinking
for Sasuke.

236
00:14:18,145 --> 00:14:20,511
A person would normally
take off the mask here.

237
00:14:20,581 --> 00:14:23,106
Never mind that.
Just be quiet, you idiot!

238
00:14:27,221 --> 00:14:30,088
Kakashi, you will die here!

239
00:14:30,558 --> 00:14:32,719
From this needle on the blowpipe arrow,

240
00:14:32,793 --> 00:14:37,025
coated with medicine I prepared
that will make you laugh uncontrollably...

241
00:14:49,810 --> 00:14:51,835
You'll die laughing...

242
00:14:52,079 --> 00:14:54,547
That is the fitting way for you...

243
00:14:55,449 --> 00:14:56,473
Darn...

244
00:14:56,550 --> 00:15:00,919
I wanted to see it too,
but this is a hot spring...

245
00:15:01,455 --> 00:15:02,683
But I want to see!

246
00:15:05,226 --> 00:15:07,126
Kakashi Sensei!
Aren't you ready yet?

247
00:15:07,194 --> 00:15:09,389
All right, I'm coming in now.

248
00:15:10,064 --> 00:15:11,053
I <i>do</i> want to see it!

249
00:15:15,503 --> 00:15:16,197
Here he comes!

250
00:15:16,404 --> 00:15:17,166
Great!

251
00:15:18,205 --> 00:15:19,968
Oh, I can't see at all!

252
00:15:34,488 --> 00:15:38,686
Thanks for waiting.
I'll just soak for a little while.

253
00:15:40,661 --> 00:15:42,424
- Why is it like this?!
- Why is it like this?!

254
00:15:42,596 --> 00:15:43,221
<i>Now!</i>

255
00:15:44,131 --> 00:15:45,928
Huh? Something wrong

256
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:48,431
And slowly, I sink in.

257
00:15:59,580 --> 00:16:01,605
What the?!

258
00:16:02,149 --> 00:16:04,845
What happened?
I want to know!

259
00:16:11,659 --> 00:16:16,653
What in the world is
Kakashi Sensei thinking? Huh?

260
00:16:24,672 --> 00:16:27,800
Darn, I'm completely flushed... Huh?

261
00:16:29,810 --> 00:16:31,334
- Our clothes are gone!
- Our clothes are gone!

262
00:16:40,855 --> 00:16:43,449
Please come again!
Please come again!

263
00:16:43,524 --> 00:16:44,491
Thank you for coming!

264
00:16:44,558 --> 00:16:47,322
Please come again!
Please come again!

265
00:16:48,229 --> 00:16:52,689
Crap... I'm going to
definitely defeat you, Kakashi Hatake.

266
00:16:52,900 --> 00:16:56,666
But it was great that
we brought spare clothes.

267
00:16:56,837 --> 00:17:00,273
I wonder who took them away...?
Our clothes!

268
00:17:01,175 --> 00:17:04,906
All right,
each of you work at your own posts.

269
00:17:05,312 --> 00:17:06,574
Now, break up.

270
00:17:08,449 --> 00:17:10,212
I can't stand it anymore...

271
00:17:10,284 --> 00:17:12,445
I have too much stress stored inside.

272
00:17:13,054 --> 00:17:15,420
I'm almost at the end of
my patience as well...

273
00:17:15,990 --> 00:17:18,618
Sasuke... actually, me too...

274
00:17:19,493 --> 00:17:22,223
Then, it's the last resort!

275
00:17:22,730 --> 00:17:24,163
- Last resort?
- Last resort?

276
00:17:25,566 --> 00:17:26,294
What is this?

277
00:17:26,367 --> 00:17:29,564
Can't you see? It's Shinobi outfit.

278
00:17:29,670 --> 00:17:31,695
When did you get this ready?

279
00:17:31,772 --> 00:17:34,332
Well, well, never mind that,
never mind that.

280
00:17:34,475 --> 00:17:35,669
What do you do with this?

281
00:17:38,045 --> 00:17:40,673
We'll strip away the mask.
Even if we have to use force!

282
00:17:46,253 --> 00:17:47,447
Darn Kakashi...

283
00:17:47,521 --> 00:17:48,715
Boss! Look at that!

284
00:17:51,392 --> 00:17:53,155
Hey, Kakashi Hatake!

285
00:17:53,694 --> 00:17:56,356
Hey, what are you guys up to?

286
00:17:56,464 --> 00:17:59,900
W-What are you talking about?
We are simply Ninja.

287
00:17:59,967 --> 00:18:02,197
It is not that we want to see
what is behind your mask!

288
00:18:02,269 --> 00:18:05,363
Fool! Don't say unnecessary things!

289
00:18:05,639 --> 00:18:06,435
That's...!

290
00:18:07,108 --> 00:18:11,135
Boss! There's somebody else besides you
who holds a grudge on Kakashi!

291
00:18:11,245 --> 00:18:12,610
Now is the chance!

292
00:18:12,813 --> 00:18:14,110
Right! Let's go

293
00:18:14,181 --> 00:18:14,840
- Right!
- Right!

294
00:18:15,683 --> 00:18:17,014
Stop right there!

295
00:18:19,887 --> 00:18:23,015
Kakashi! It's time for you
to pay for your crime!

296
00:18:24,125 --> 00:18:25,023
You shall die!

297
00:18:25,092 --> 00:18:29,290
With this medicine I prepared
that will make you cry... What?!

298
00:18:31,866 --> 00:18:35,427
Oh, just when I thought how long
you guys were going to sneak around...

299
00:18:36,270 --> 00:18:38,204
you finally come out.

300
00:18:38,372 --> 00:18:40,169
Ah, well, you know...

301
00:18:40,908 --> 00:18:43,433
But before that,
Sasuke, Sakura, Naruto!

302
00:18:45,279 --> 00:18:47,440
Why are you guys dressed like that?

303
00:18:47,715 --> 00:18:50,047
Huh?! Well, yeah, so...

304
00:18:50,684 --> 00:18:51,673
<i>Oh no...</i>

305
00:18:51,752 --> 00:18:53,811
<i>We have to make up an explanation,</i>
<i>whatever it is!</i>

306
00:18:54,788 --> 00:18:55,880
Caught you!

307
00:18:56,123 --> 00:19:00,560
We were well aware that
you three were targeting Kakashi Sensei!

308
00:19:00,728 --> 00:19:06,223
What?! Then our plot was exposed
from the beginning!

309
00:19:06,433 --> 00:19:10,335
Of course!
This was a trap to lure you guys out!

310
00:19:10,404 --> 00:19:12,065
We caught you off guard!

311
00:19:12,139 --> 00:19:14,664
So we were completely caught
in the trap.

312
00:19:14,742 --> 00:19:17,768
Darn! We underestimated you,
thinking it was kids!

313
00:19:18,345 --> 00:19:20,040
<i>I never heard that story!</i>

314
00:19:20,447 --> 00:19:21,880
<i>Nice, Sakura!</i>

315
00:19:22,183 --> 00:19:26,711
I don't quite get what's happening,
but oh well...

316
00:19:30,257 --> 00:19:31,451
- Please forgive us!
- Please forgive us!

317
00:19:33,327 --> 00:19:34,817
There's no use talking...

318
00:19:35,329 --> 00:19:37,229
- O-Oh no!
- S-Stop!

319
00:19:44,572 --> 00:19:46,904
It's the same as three years ago!

320
00:19:46,974 --> 00:19:51,638
This time, we're hung by just one rope,
combined with the same movement.

321
00:19:51,712 --> 00:19:54,374
By the way, who are you guys?

322
00:19:54,448 --> 00:19:57,076
- And he doesn't even remember us!
- And he doesn't even remember us!

323
00:20:04,325 --> 00:20:05,952
Hey, Kakashi Sensei.

324
00:20:06,560 --> 00:20:07,390
Yeah?

325
00:20:07,528 --> 00:20:09,996
What is behind that mask?

326
00:20:10,164 --> 00:20:12,724
What? You wanted to see
what's behind this mask?

327
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:13,562
Yeah!

328
00:20:13,634 --> 00:20:15,602
Then you should have said
that from the beginning...

329
00:20:15,936 --> 00:20:17,995
Well, can you show us?

330
00:20:18,439 --> 00:20:19,599
I don't mind...

331
00:20:19,673 --> 00:20:20,469
What the?!

332
00:20:20,741 --> 00:20:22,140
Sure thing.

333
00:20:25,613 --> 00:20:26,875
All right...

334
00:20:30,484 --> 00:20:31,576
<i>Is it like cod roe?</i>

335
00:20:35,256 --> 00:20:36,223
<i>Buckteeth?</i>

336
00:20:39,526 --> 00:20:41,118
<i>Or a tiny mouth?</i>

337
00:20:41,362 --> 00:20:43,330
Behind this mask...

338
00:20:43,564 --> 00:20:45,259
- <i>Behind that mask...</i>
- <i>Behind that mask...</i>

339
00:20:47,968 --> 00:20:50,436
There happens to be another mask!

340
00:20:50,871 --> 00:20:52,065
- What?!
- What?!

341
00:20:56,777 --> 00:20:57,903
What?!

342
00:20:58,679 --> 00:21:00,909
What in the world is that?!

343
00:21:06,987 --> 00:21:11,686
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

344
00:21:11,759 --> 00:21:16,093
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

345
00:21:16,697 --> 00:21:20,224
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

346
00:21:21,468 --> 00:21:25,928
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

347
00:21:26,106 --> 00:21:31,544
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

348
00:21:32,046 --> 00:21:36,346
<i>That hold us together</i>

349
00:21:36,817 --> 00:21:46,055
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

350
00:21:46,126 --> 00:21:48,720
<i>you say laughingly</i>

351
00:21:48,962 --> 00:21:54,628
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

352
00:21:55,202 --> 00:21:59,571
<i>Like a comet,</i>

353
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:05,738
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

354
00:22:05,813 --> 00:22:12,912
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

355
00:22:13,921 --> 00:22:23,296
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

356
00:22:24,631 --> 00:22:32,163
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

357
00:22:32,239 --> 00:22:36,232
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

358
00:22:38,946 --> 00:22:41,312
Begging your pardon!
Begging your pardon!

359
00:22:41,515 --> 00:22:45,315
I was born and raised in the Leaf Village
in the Land of Fire.

360
00:22:45,486 --> 00:22:47,511
My given name is Naruto,
and the surname is Uzumaki.

361
00:22:47,588 --> 00:22:48,247
People call me...

362
00:22:48,322 --> 00:22:49,380
"The No. 1 Hyperactive
Knucklehead Ninja "!

363
00:22:49,456 --> 00:22:51,321
I'm not "the No. 1 Hyperactive
Knucklehead Ninja"!

364
00:22:51,392 --> 00:22:53,860
What's this
you've been practicing?

365
00:22:54,027 --> 00:22:56,461
We're going to meet with
Boss Wasabi.

366
00:22:56,663 --> 00:22:59,393
A proper first greeting's important!

367
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:04,903
Next time: "Mission:
Help an Old Friend in the Land of Tea!"
